  Locus:
    Page: 420
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Self-Reliance
---
You are your own physician. You are your own savior and redeemer. Nobody
can give you freedom. You will have to tread the spiritual path yourself.
Rely on your own self-exertion. Teachers and books can only help you to a
certain extent
